This Home Offers 4 Bedrooms, Large Eat-In Kitchen, First Floor Bath, Half Bath on 2nd Level, Original Hardwood Floors, Oil or Electric Heating, Shed, detached 1 Car Garage, Semi-Attached 2 Car Garage, Laundry in Basement, Fenced in Backyard and More!!!  The sellers are the 2nd owners on this home that was built in the 50's which says it all...
